# CartWave Backend — Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in the values before running the application.

```env
# ── Database ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
DATABASE_URL=jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5432/cartwave
DB_USERNAME=cartwave
DB_PASSWORD=your_db_password

# ── JWT ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
JWT_SECRET=change-me-to-a-long-random-secret-at-least-32-chars
JWT_ACCESS_EXPIRATION_MS=900000
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRATION_MS=604800000

# ── SMTP ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USERNAME=your@email.com
SMTP_PASSWORD=your_smtp_password
SMTP_AUTH=true
SMTP_STARTTLS=true

# ── AWS S3 (product image uploads) ───────────────────────────────────────────
AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=AKIAIOSFODNN7EXAMPLE
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=wJalrXUtnFEMI/K7MDENG/bPxRfiCYEXAMPLEKEY
AWS_REGION=eu-west-1
AWS_S3_BUCKET_NAME=cartwave-assets
AWS_S3_BASE_URL=https://cartwave-assets.s3.eu-west-1.amazonaws.com

# ── CORS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000,https://yourdomain.com

# ── Scheduled Jobs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
JOB_EMAIL_DISPATCH_MS=30000
JOB_ESCROW_RELEASE_CRON=0 0 2 * * *
JOB_SUBSCRIPTION_EXPIRATION_CRON=0 0 * * * *
JOB_KPI_AGGREGATION_CRON=0 */30 * * * *
JOB_FRAUD_SCAN_CRON=0 */10 * * * *

# ── Server ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PORT=8080
```
